1>> install epel                           // repository of mosquitto

2>> install mosquitto                     // to install mosquitto

3>> systemctl start mosquitto.service    // to start mosquitto service

4>> systemctl stop firewalld.service      // to stop firewall if any firewall is actinve and you want to connect different sysste(ip addredd)

5>> npm install mqtt  (to install globally put " -g ")  
